<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Sellers - DomaHub</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./css/main_sellers.css" />
    <%- include("../templates/head_links"); %>
  </head>

<body>

  <%- include("../templates/navbar", {user: user}); %>

  <section class="hero is-accent gradient-left-right is-medium">
    <div class="hero-body">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="column">
          <h1 class="title is-2">
            Don't just let your domains sit, <br />
            let them work for you.
          </h1>
          <h2 class="subtitle is-4 is-light">
            Generate revenue by listing with DomaHub
          </h2>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section is-medium">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column">
          <div class="content">
            <h2>How much could you make with DomaHub?</h2>
          </div>
          <nav class="level">
            <div class="level-left">
              <div class="level-item">
                <label class="label">Number of Domains</label>
                <p class="control">
                  <input id="num-domains-value" class="input earnings-input" type="number" value="1" min="1" placeholder="Enter a number"/>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="level-item">
                <label class="label">Rate</label>
                <p class="control">
                  <span class="select">
                    <select id="time-value" class="earnings-input">
                      <option selected value="720">Hourly</option>
                      <option value="30">Daily</option>
                      <option value="4">Weekly</option>
                      <option value="1">Monthly</option>
                      <option value=".0833">Yearly</option>
                    </select>
                  </span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="level-item">
                <label class="label">Price</label>
                <p class="control has-icon">
                  <input id="price-value" class="input earnings-input" type="number" value="1" min="1" placeholder="Enter a number"/>
                  <i class="fa fa-dollar"></i>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="level-item box is-accent has-text-centered">
                <div class="content">
                  <h2 id="earnings-potential" class="is-white is-bold">&#36 0</h2>
                  <p class="is-white">
                    Per Month!
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </nav>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column margin-bottom-25">
          <div class="content">
            <h1 class="title has-text-centered is-2">
              How to List on DomaHub
            </h1>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column">
          <div class="content margin-bottom-25">
            <h2 class="has-styleborderBottom">Signing up.</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-one-quarter">
          <div class="content">
            <figure class="image left-aligned is-48x48">
              <img src="/images/lib/material/user-outline.svg" alt="User">
            </figure>
            <h3 class="is-bold">Create a DomaHub account</h3>
            <p>
              Creating an account with us is completely free.
              <a class="orange-link" href="/signup" title="Sign Up">Sign up</a>
              using a valid email address and check your email afterwards
              to verify your account.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-one-quarter">
          <div class="content">
            <figure class="image left-aligned is-48x48">
              <img src="/images/lib/material/creditcard.svg" alt="Payment">
            </figure>
            <h3 class="is-bold">Authorize Stripe payments</h3>
            <p>
              In order to receive and make payments, you must
              <a class="orange-link" href="/authorizestripe" title="Authorize Stripe">authorize Stripe</a>
              in your account settings. Stripe is a secure third-party platform
              for online transactions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column">
          <div class="content margin-bottom-25">
            <h2 class="has-styleborderBottom">Creating listings.</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-one-quarter">
          <div class="content">
            <figure class="image left-aligned is-48x48">
              <img src="/images/lib/material/website.svg" alt="Listing">
            </figure>
            <h3 class="is-bold">List your domain</h3>
            <p>
              <a class="orange-link" href="/listing/create" title="Create Listing">Create a listing</a>
              for your domain name(s). A listing must have a description
              and may optionally have a background image and purchase link.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-one-quarter">
          <div class="content">
            <figure class="image left-aligned is-48x48">
              <img src="/images/lib/material/layers.svg" alt="Listing">
            </figure>
            <h3 class="is-bold">Choose Basic or Premium</h3>
            <p>
              A listing can be one of two different types: <strong>Basic or Premium</strong>.
              This must be defined during the listing process. Please see section below
              for a detailed description of the two types.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-one-quarter">
          <div class="content">
            <figure class="image left-aligned is-48x48">
              <img src="/images/lib/material/dns.svg" alt="Listing">
            </figure>
            <h3 class="is-bold">Redirect your DNS server</h3>
            <p>
              You must
              <a class="orange-link" href="/faq#verifying" title="Point your DNS">point your DNS server</a>
              to our servers (click the link for instructions). This step is necessary to verify that you are the
              owner of this domain.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="basicvpremium" class="section is-medium">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column margin-bottom-25">
          <div class="content">
            <h1 class="title has-text-centered is-2">
              Basic vs. Premium Listings
            </h1>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-2">
        </div>
        <div class="column is-4">
          <div class="card is-fullwidth">
            <header class="card-header is-accent">
              <h2 class="card-header-title has-text-centered">
                Basic
              </h2>
            </header>
            <div class="card-content">
              <div class="content">
                <ul>
                  <li class="has-icon is-medium">
                    <span class="icon is-medium is-accent">
                      <i class="fa fa-gift"></i>
                    </span>
                    <span>Completely free to list</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="has-icon is-medium">
                    <span class="icon is-medium is-accent">
                      <i class="fa fa-handshake-o"></i>
                    </span>
                    <span>15% commission taken</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="has-icon is-medium">
                    <span class="icon is-medium is-accent">
                      <i class="fa fa-lock"></i>
                    </span>
                    <span>Fixed pricing options</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="has-icon is-medium">
                    <span class="icon is-medium is-accent">
                      <i class="fa fa-ban"></i>
                    </span>
                    <span>Hourly pricing unavailable</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-4">
          <div class="card is-fullwidth">
            <header class="card-header is-primary">
              <h2 class="card-header-title has-text-centered">
                Premium
              </h2>
            </header>
              <div class="card-content">
                <div class="content">
                  <ul>
                    <li class="has-icon is-medium">
                      <span class="icon is-medium is-primary">
                        <i class="fa fa-usd"></i>
                      </span>
                      <span>&#36;5 per month to list</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="has-icon is-medium">
                      <span class="icon is-medium is-primary">
                        <i class="fa fa-thumbs-o-up"></i>
                      </span>
                      <span>NO commission taken</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="has-icon is-medium">
                      <span class="icon is-medium is-primary">
                        <i class="fa fa-circle-o-notch"></i>
                      </span>
                      <span>Custom, flexible pricing options</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="has-icon is-medium">
                      <span class="icon is-medium is-primary">
                        <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                      </span>
                      <span>Hourly pricing available</span>
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="columns">
          <div class="column is-2">

          </div>
          <div class="column is-8">
            <div class="content">
              <h3 class="is-bold">Which type is right for my domain?</h3>
              <p>
                If you are not sure about the quality or value of your domain,
                we recommend selecting a Basic listing. On the other hand, if you
                believe your domain is highly valuable, you will see better
                benefits from posting a Premium listing.
              </p>
              <h3 class="is-bold">What does fixed pricing mean?</h3>
              <p>
                It means you will not be able to decide the pricing for
                a Basic listing. The prices will be set at the default rates.
              </p>
              <h3 class="is-bold">What are the default rates?</h3>
              <p>
                  <li>$10 / day.</li>
                  <li>$25 / week.</li>
                  <li>$50 / month.</li>
              </p>
              <h3 class="is-bold">What is hourly pricing?</h3>
              <p>
                Hourly pricing allows you to rent out a domain name by the hour.
              </p>
              <p>If you have any other questions, please check out our <a href="/faq" class="orange-link">FAQ</a>!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section margin-bottom-50">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content has-text-centered">
        <h2>Ready to start selling?</h2>
        <a class="button is-accent is-large" href="/listing/create">Create Listing</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include("../templates/footer"); %>
  <%- include("../templates/js_scripts"); %>
  <script src="/js/routes/main/main_seller_logic.js" type="text/javascript"></script>

  </body>
</html>
